description:
A dating app for your photos & videos

PhotoSwooper is a dating app for your photos & videos.

Have you ever had too many photos/videos to sort through and would just love to swipe on them like dating profiles? Well I made just the app: PhotoSwooper. :D


Features:

  • Undo button
  • Info drawer
  • Review swiped photos/videos before they are deleted
  • Statistics
  • Customisable with many preferences
  • No ads, forever!

Hope you enjoy!
